    "title": "Principal Visual Merchandiser at Poorvika Mobiles",
    "description": "If you're a passionate Visual Merchandiser with drive and ambition, Poorvika Mobiles in Raipur is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Poorvika Mobiles:\nPoorvika Mobiles is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Build relationships with regular customers to drive loyalty\n• Manage store operations to ensure smooth daily functioning\n• Maintain high standards of store hygiene and cleanliness\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n• Manage shrinkage and reduce stock discrepancies\n• Achieve sales targets and improve store performance metrics\n• Implement promotional activities and in-store campaigns\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Planogram\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n• Proficiency in Retail Analytics\n• Proficiency in Loyalty Programs\n• Proficiency in E-commerce Integration\n• Proficiency in Team Leadership\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n• Proficiency in Shrinkage Control\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Raipur, Chhattisgarh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Poorvika Mobiles!",
